{"tid":1432083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港島東大遊行】文宣手足入黎攞貨","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:32:12.000Z","uid":66023,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd21cfd3f35731ce3b74deccce9498b582c556f6","tid":1432083,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"大家好我地係811港島東大遊行既搞手，現階段不反對通知書既所有申請手續已經做哂，只係警方遲遲未有結果，不過我地已經整好好冠唔同既宣傳圖，單張都已經開街站派緊，希望大家幫手share下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">811港島東大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊行路線由維園出發往渣華道遊樂場<br />\n8月11日下午一點維園集合，一點半出發<br />\n<br />\n踩參最深紅嘅社區 集結最強大嘅抗爭力量<br />\n<br />\n📍重申5大訴求<br />\n撤回引渡修例<br />\n收回暴動定性<br />\n撤銷義士控罪<br />\n追究警察濫權<br />\n實行真雙普選<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n深入建制腹地 香港靠晒你地！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n811港島東遊行公海Group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AylQ7VSsAArHphDEXeSflA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAylQ7VSsAArHphDEXeSflA&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO75S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=15d4a384\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AylQ7VSsAArHphDEXeSflA</a><br />\n811港島東遊行Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkeast811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkeast811&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO75S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=df497718\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkeast811</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">無懼警黑白色恐怖，全民集結，還我香港</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6z5w6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6z5w6R.jpg&h=30deac0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vb1C7EV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVb1C7EV.jpg&h=a99d7b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTsrgxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTsrgxN.jpg&h=73aaaaa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5oNLq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5oNLq8.jpg&h=7bafd32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRPhocP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRPhocP.jpg&h=7582134c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qqDR6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qqDR6a.jpg&h=bcffbd93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f493c61a3b63805c89a7022ea7079b697ede51c","tid":1432083,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ed9d9f91b9a35cb87320ff2c5d23fa7773e5d3","tid":1432083,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea8db6dcc7a0d82ba6f17dda70ae9006d9db452","tid":1432083,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908e32e23fc1956adf653f7d31b03648e03c328d","tid":1432083,"uid":66023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8b277a3bcb910c1390d873bdf7bd950e45cd61","tid":1432083,"uid":10503,"